
'''= center and incubator for Social and Cooperative Entrepreneurship in Brussels, Belgium'''

URL: http://coopcity.be/


=Description=

"Coopcity is a center for Social and Cooperative Entrepreneurship in Brussels. They support Brussels-based entrepreneurial initiatives with high societal added value and is particularly interested in the needs of emerging collective projects. Through its various coaching programs, COOPCITY helps project promoters to put together their ideas. It also supports existing social enterprises in the development of their activities. Furthermore, COOPCITY wants to instill a different view of the economy and aims to inform, educate and inspire future entrepreneurs on social entrepreneurship in Brussels. Finally, through its various programs and activities, COOPCITY aspires to propose an environment conducive to cooperation and collaboration between the various actors, working within social entrepreneurship in Brussels."



